{"about_the_game":"<strong>Awaken from a coma with no memory after a tragic car accident that took your family. Immerse yourself in a 1-4 player cooperative horror experience, navigating haunting nightmares and facing unique monsters. As you delve deeper into each nightmare, challenges intensify, offering greater risks and rewards.<br><br>Survive intense encounters with deadly monsters and environments using a variety of tools and tactics in the nightmares. Discover and collect lucidity crystals, valuable assets in the astral plane. Strategically sacrifice them to manipulate and alter upcoming nightmares.<br><br>Piece together your forgotten past through these nightmares, but proceed with caution. As the line between dream and reality blurs, maintaining your sanity is essential. Will you uncover the mysteries with your sanity intact?</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2673910/extras/nightmares-monsters.png?t=1728669807\" /><br>Explore a series of unique nightmares, each growing in intensity and featuring a diverse range of monsters. As challenges increase, so do the rewards. Encounter numerous terrifying monsters, each with its own behaviors, strengths, and distinct senses, ensuring dynamic and unpredictable confrontations. Adapt and strategize to survive against these varied threats.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2673910/extras/monstergif_616x229.gif?t=1728669807\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2673910/extras/tools-items.png?t=1728669807\" /><br>Sacrifice and strategize with currencies collected from previous nightmares to enhance survival chances. Spend wisely in the Astral Plane to influence future nightmares, alter traps, and increase the chances of valuable item spawns. Utilize these resources to improve vision, open new paths, distract enemies, 